  "Description": {
    "English": "A device specifically crafted to keep lifeforms alive for thousands of years longer than their natural lifespan. Such a device requires great skill to manufacture, as not only is it technically complex, but the consequences for a user in the event of malfunction would be disastrous.<br><br>Crafted from <span class=\"name name-technology\">Quantum Processors</span>, <span class=\"name name-technology\">Cryogenic Chambers</span>, and <span class=\"name name-special\">Iridesite</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "能使生命体比其自然寿命多存活几千年的设备。这种设备需要高超的技术制造，不仅技术复杂，而且一旦发生故障，将对使用者造成毁灭性影响。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-technology\">量子处理器</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">低温舱</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">辐矿</span>制作。",
    "TencentChinese": "能使生命体比其自然寿命多存活几千年的设备。这种设备需要高超的技术制造，不仅技术复杂，而且一旦发生故障，将对使用者造成难以预估的影响。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-technology\">量子处理器</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">低温舱</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">辐矿</span>制作。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特地製造來讓生命體活得比自然生命週期長上數千年的裝置。此裝置不僅科技繁複，故障的話還會對使用者產生災難性的後果，因此其製造需要高超技術。<br><br>可使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">量子處理器</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">低溫艙</span>與<span class=\"name name-special\">霓虹石</span>製造。"
  },
