    "SimplifiedChinese": "非常先进的制作产品。通过突袭<span class=\"name name-technology\">行星工厂</span>或在<span class=\"name name-special\">太空异象</span>上的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">合成实验室</span>学习相关设计图。<br>由<span class=\"name name-commodity\">量子处理器</span>、<span class=\"name name-commodity\">低温舱</span>和<span class=\"name name-commodity\">辐矿</span>制作而成。",
